data.description: You are going to FALL in LOVE with this beautiful all-brick, 4-bed, 3-bath home  (plus office) located in the lovely gated neighborhood of Cottonwood. It has over 2800 square feet of living space on a half acre lot, not far from NAS Whiting Field. Outdoor amenities include a covered back patio. You'll love the extra room in the three-car garage with side entry. In addition to the foyer with hall closet, the office and formal dining room are situated in the front of the home and feature beautiful hardwood flooring. At the heart of the home you'll find the great room with gas fireplace and kitchen with granite countertops, contemporary tile backsplash, stainless-steel appliances, pantry, and breakfast nook. The master bedroom is HUGE. This home is a must see!!!
